      "instruction": "<p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1723209004035-x200.jpg",
