    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your<strong> Thai-style pork belly moo hong </strong>with the <strong>baked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
